{"tid":654435,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2007年　浸大加設普通話畢業要求　同年　語常會撥款2億落實25年內全面普教中","createTime":"2018-05-05T15:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T16:28:47.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"71f36ca5c839a3866d213d88ca1bc2be7c9d22a7","tid":654435,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:46:50.000Z","msg":"第一階段2008-2018<br />\n<br />\n小四至中三<br />\n<br />\n?學校以不同程度開展用普通話教中文。<br />\n<br />\n?學校向語常會申請「以普 通話 教授中國語文科計畫」。<br />\n<br />\n?到2018年，絕大部分學校以不同程度推行用普通話教中文。<br />\n<br />\n第二階段2018-2028<br />\n<br />\n小四至中三<br />\n<br />\n?全港學校必須在高小和初中階段推行用普通話教中文。<br />\n<br />\n?用普通話教中文的班數不可少於50%，並於10年內逐步提升至100%。<br />\n<br />\n?到2028年，高小和初中全面用普通話教中文。<br />\n<br />\n第三階段2028-2033<br />\n<br />\n小一至中六<br />\n<br />\n?全港學校必須在初小和高中階段推行用普通話教中文。<br />\n<br />\n?到2033年，中小學全面用普通話教中文。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.huayuqiao.org/DOC8900/8908.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.huayuqiao.org%2FDOC8900%2F8908.htm&d=%2FRFxZqydoyRPSCHSLSDlZ7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=bdae1d8c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.huayuqiao.org/DOC8900/8908.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8dc2eb0c0ee969e2f6bca2d5247b6d88d03f7a1e","tid":654435,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T21:37:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6172bd33b935cc879b2f1f1261341bee8f2fd8bf","tid":654435,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T06:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a8885545aa4e556ba6d363a7e06363d05f6e38","tid":654435,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T06:50:38.000Z","msg":"第一階段已經完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee30bb3607626adb92132e47608bc2e0c522905c","tid":654435,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T07:55:29.000Z